\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The script we got about how to plant and start a church\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Need to borrow a whole lot of money or have a church backing you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Need to launch on the right days (Easter was not one of them)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Need to have a worship leader in place\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}4 out of 5 fail to begin with\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}1 in 10 church plants don\'92t ever get past 100 people\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The list went on and one\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We did everything wrong or different\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When you start something all you have is hope and a dream and that is what I had when we started River Lake Church\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
