\f2\fs18 \cf2 \super 9\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So the king of Israel set out with the king of Judah and the king of Edom.\'a0After a roundabout march of seven days, the army had no more water for themselves or for the animals with them.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93What!\'94 exclaimed the king of Israel. \'93Has the\'a0Lord\'a0called us three kings together only to deliver us into the hands of Moab?\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question #1 \'96 Where\'92s the desert in your life?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s dry, it\'92s dead, it is hard to get through the day in that area\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 11\'a0
