An officer of the king of Israel answered, \'93Elisha\'a0son of Shaphat is here. He used to pour water on the hands of Elijah.
\fs15 \super [\ul b\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 12\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jehoshaphat said, \'93The word\'a0of the\'a0Lord\'a0is with him.\'94 So the king of Israel and Jehoshaphat and the king of Edom went down to him.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 13\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Elisha said to the king of Israel, \'93Why do you want to involve me? Go to the prophets of your father and the prophets of your mother.\'94\
\'93No,\'94 the king of Israel answered, \'93because it was the\'a0Lord\'a0who called us three kings together to deliver us into the hands of Moab.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Elisha said, \'93As surely as the\'a0Lord\'a0Almighty lives, whom I serve, if I did not have respect for the presence of Jehoshaphat king of Judah, I would not pay any attention to you.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 15\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But now bring me a harpist.\'94\
While the harpist was playing, the hand\'a0of the\'a0Lord\'a0came on Elisha\'a0\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 16\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He said, \'93Thus says the\'a0Lord, \'91Make this valley full of trenches.\'92\'a0 (NASB)\
