\ls11\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Faith requires knowing your role and executing it, not knowing the results and expecting it.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f3\b0 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To receive the blessing of the ditch you first have to dig it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So today, just like roughly 2 years ago I\'92m standing on a stage\'85refusing to believe the script we\'92ve been given.  Trusting that God is going to do something amazing and provide for us in ways we can\'92t imagine if we are faithful.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Will you join me on the journey to see what God wants to do through you in this community!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
